msgid ""
"The &krdc; project has been started by Tim Jansen <email>tim@tjansen.de</"
"email>. As a Google Summer of Code 2007 project, Urs Wolfer <email>uwolfer @ "
"kde.org</email> has completely rewritten &krdc;. Thanks to Google for making "
"this possible, and thanks to the great mentor of this Summer of Code "
"project, &Brad.Hards; &Brad.Hards.mail;."
msgstr ""
"O projeto do &krdc; foi iniciado por Tim Jansen <email>tim@tjansen.de</"
"email>. Como um projeto do Google Summer of Code 2007, o Urs Wolfer "
"<email>uwolfer @ kde.org</email> reorganizou novamente o &krdc;. Obrigado ao "
"Google por tornar isto possível, e muito obrigado ao grande mentor deste "
"projeto do Summer of Code, o &Brad.Hards; &Brad.Hards.mail;."

